{"tid":1883912,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ff系列 - 想借庫","createTime":"2020-02-17T09:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T14:15:00.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95b44ad953fca70acf30574dbbbc53904129bc0b","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"有冇觀音大士想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/02/20200211_%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AF%E4%B8%89%E9%99%A2_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F02%2F20200211_%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2599%25A2_3.jpg&h=b7012a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/02/20200211_%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AF%E4%B8%89%E9%99%A2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F02%2F20200211_%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2599%25A2_1.jpg&h=f5242d1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99d0490871b2f040fdf0b5bc1bf823cecfeeac0a","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"紅磡觀音廟笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c42ed3f4b64c6599415eb6c92251dab3b3dfda","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"善信於借庫時應準備好紅燭1對、大香3支、細香1扎、金銀衣紙1份及金花1對、五齋（羅漢齋）或五果（蘋果、橙、提子、雪梨、士多啤梨等）、茶3杯、水3杯以及筷子3對。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20200215/photo/bkn-20200215090011181-0215_00982_001_04b.jpg?20200215125707\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20200215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200215090011181-0215_00982_001_04b.jpg%3F20200215125707&h=5c4f3220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.事前應茹素<br />\n觀音是茹素的，所以祭品不應有肉，參拜者在借庫前一天最好食齋，借庫當日也應全日齋戒，以示虔誠。<br />\n2.衣飾要樸素<br />\n入廟借庫，宜用碌柚葉沖乾淨身體，再換上乾淨樸素的衣服，切勿穿得太光鮮或太暴露，更不可穿金戴銀和戴帽。欲求增強健康運勢者，男性宜穿啡色的服飾；女性宜穿米黃色或橙色的服飾。<br />\n3.肖龍者刑沖<br />\n正月廿六日屬狗日，對生肖屬「龍」的人士有刑沖，如往廟宇借庫，必須佩戴綠玉「兔」，以化解刑剋。<br />\n4.依廟祝指示<br />\n借庫的手續，每間觀音廟均有指定程序，只要依照廟祝的指示便可。祈求時，心中點禱應稱呼「觀音大士」這個正名，不應用「娘娘」、「菩薩」等別號。<br />\n5.只能求正財<br />\n祈求觀音大士庇祐今年財運亨通，財運只能是正財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以稟神時應祈求今年能夠獲取應得錢財，不應貪心。如求觀音賜福，必須端正態度，不可以存妄念、邪念，必須誠懇。<br />\n6.拿走還神花<br />\n借完庫後，記得將「還神花」攞走放在家中窗前，最好插在今年流年財位（即西北方）。至於借庫後獲得的利是（即「庫錢」），應放在銀包或手袋，妥為保存，在還庫時連同還庫壽金化回庫房。"},{"pid":"2c45163ac2bc0dcb4f31a490c8b130376a0dfa48","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/images/stories/288/2020/02/17022020comicimage0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F288%2F2020%2F02%2F17022020comicimage0.jpeg&h=2083ba90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">???</span>"},{"pid":"62e50235eb6e82b74f2b4c4e72c05cc611df0346","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef445d63d95fa2a48d2ce15ac6df0cb014e8be2","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62e50235eb6e82b74f2b4c4e72c05cc611df0346","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"有冇清john?"},{"pid":"16844264a31b55490463bae33447a40374e2da8c","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef445d63d95fa2a48d2ce15ac6df0cb014e8be2","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62e50235eb6e82b74f2b4c4e72c05cc611df0346","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"有冇清john?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">批准</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b217fe08f0bccd3cb3ac93ffbded289cfe87a42","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16844264a31b55490463bae33447a40374e2da8c","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef445d63d95fa2a48d2ce15ac6df0cb014e8be2","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62e50235eb6e82b74f2b4c4e72c05cc611df0346","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"有冇清john?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">批准</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74263d859e0b2e5623281b25208498a961e41476","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc8afedd71de32ac3a45c940aab94ac01bf4d97","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22c124057a39719db48d8f301d32360a3ad35c9","tid":1883912,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38142bc8ac0af221fc3eef4c7bd2f964efb013d","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc8afedd71de32ac3a45c940aab94ac01bf4d97","tid":1883912,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474a93c50ca74b7637a38c46a9a60ffdfbc57710","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22c124057a39719db48d8f301d32360a3ad35c9","tid":1883912,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/85052731_2820768797983644_2882916842328817664_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=9Wmr2AyMNEgAX9AME47&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=1dbc209f7be2f2811a1fbf1e6298c9f0&amp;oe=5EC998B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F85052731_2820768797983644_2882916842328817664_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3D9Wmr2AyMNEgAX9AME47%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D1dbc209f7be2f2811a1fbf1e6298c9f0%26oe%3D5EC998B2&h=77ed285a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n********** 觀音開庫 2020 **********<br />\n農曆正月廿六日<br />\n2月18日(星期二):晚上11時至凌晨2時<br />\n2月19日(星期三):早上7時至下午7時<br />\n-----------------------------------<br />\n茶果嶺天后宮內除了敬奉天后之外，也設有觀音殿敬奉觀音，每年觀音開庫日必定香火鼎盛，眾多善信誠心前來向觀音借庫，祈求菩薩賜予平安、健康和財庫。<br />\n<br />\n【特別安排】<br />\n因應武漢肺炎疫情，觀音開庫日當天會實行人流管制措施，以免廟內過於擠迫。善信請耐心等候進廟。<br />\n<br />\n善信敬請保持戴上口罩。由於口罩供應緊張，抱歉我們未能為善信提供。請見諒。建議善信能夠預備多一個口罩，必要時贈予其他有需要的善信。發揮香港人團結互助精神。<br />\n<br />\n若未能於當天前來借庫，可請我們代辦。2月16日截止登記，額滿即止。詳情請以WhatsApp查詢。￼<br />\n（WhatsApp： 5626 2792￼）￼<br />\n<br />\n【流程】<br />\n善信於當日請先到本廟的售賣處購買一份借庫香燭，然後耐心排隊輪侯入廟。入廟後請依循工作人員指示有序地誠心向觀音菩薩借庫。<br />\n<br />\n【還庫】<br />\n借庫後善信請於農歷新年前還神答謝觀音菩薩庇佑。上年有借庫還未還庫的善信請盡快於開庫日之前先還庫。<br />\n<br />\n【還庫提示】<br />\n若你擔心自己年尾忘記還庫，你可以用WhatsApp發一個「1」字短訊給我們，我們在年底會經WhatsApp提醒你。（WhatsApp: 5626 2792）"},{"pid":"825f439995cba3365e39567ec99b3e1d00939918","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8324cad58335aa0019befa2cdf9c721683c1b036","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3ade272fff8ad63cd8aef5fe5dba0f493321ad","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"1)華人廟宇委員會轄下<br />\n&mdash;紅磡觀音廟「觀音開庫」活動取消<br />\n&mdash;銅鑼灣大坑蓮花宮及筲箕灣天后廟<br />\n今日（18日）晚上11時通宵開放至翌日（2月19日）下午6時正。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2)其他舉行觀音借庫活動廟宇<br />\n‧筲箕灣譚公廟<br />\n‧香港仔天后廟<br />\n‧黄泥涌譚公天后廟<br />\n‧土瓜灣天后廟<br />\n‧茶果嶺天后廟<br />\n‧深水埗天后廟<br />\n‧深水埗三太子<br />\n‧北帝廟和灣仔玉虛宮（北帝廟）<br />\n<br />\n3)東華三院轄下廟宇不設通宵時段<br />\n‧上環列聖宮<br />\n‧慈雲山觀音佛堂<br />\n‧旺角水月宮<br />\n‧油麻地天后廟<br />\n‧油麻地福德祠<br />\n‧油麻地社壇"},{"pid":"a54858c5aa0db4ba00ca4c1b8cd506819a2050cb","tid":1883912,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRpohn4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRpohn4.gif&h=eb4bdb89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c5d950e00dd96b741fcbb24998dfb761a59ab87","tid":1883912,"uid":136849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"八卦一問<br />\n有冇巴絲今日去左油麻地觀音廟"}]}